                <h1 class="text-gray-800 text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Breathe</h1>
                <p class="text-gray-700">Breathing techniques are simple yet effective tools that can help manage anxiety and stress, particularly for individuals experiencing symptoms of PTSD. By focusing on our breath, we can ground ourselves in the present moment, reduce tension, and cultivate a sense of calm.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="w-1/2 pl-4 text-center">
                <img src="https://medicaldialogues.in/h-upload/2021/09/13/1500x900_160337-untitled-design-1.webp" alt="Breathing Exercise" class="mb-4 mx-auto rounded-md shadow-lg">
